@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Upload Profile Picture

start
:Applicant uploads profile picture;
:Frontend sends POST /api/profile/upload-picture with Bearer token;
:Server validates image data;
:Server uploads image to Cloudinary;
if (Upload failed?) then (yes)
  :Return 500 "Upload failed";
  stop
else (no)
  :Update profile with picture URL in database;
  :Return 200 with image URL;
  :Frontend displays uploaded image;
endif
stop

@enduml
